oleon|year=2010|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-0-203-82830-4|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Lynn|first=John A.|authorlink=John A. Lynn|title=The Wars of Louis XIV 1667\u20131714|year=2013|publisher=[[Routledge]]|isbn=9781317899518|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yy9mAgAAQBAJ|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Mintzker|first=Yair|title=The Defortification of the German City, 1689\u20131866|year=2012|publisher=[[Cambridge University]] [[Cambridge University Press|Press]]|isbn=9781107024038|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=xLhiazIO9B0C|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Pevsner|first=Nikolaus|authorlink=Nikolaus Pevsner|title=An Outline of European Architecture|year=1948|publisher=[[Pelican Books]]|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Rott|first1=Hans|last2=Kraus|first2=Franz Xaver|title=Die Kunstdenkm\u00e4ler des Grossherzogthums Baden: Die Kunstdenkm\u00e4ler des Amtsbezirks Bruchsal (Kreis Karlsruhe)|language=de|volume=9|year=1913|publisher=Verlag von J.C.B. Mohr|url=https://digi.ub.uni-heidelberg.de/diglit/kdm9bd2|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Templer|first=John|title=The Staircase: History and Theories|year=1995|publisher=[[MIT Press]]|edition=Illustrated|isbn=0262700557|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hwnQYdhIHDwC|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Whaley|first=Joachim|title=Germany and the Holy Roman Empire: From the Peace of Westphalia to the Dissolution of the Reich|year=2012|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-969307-8|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Wilson|first=Peter H.|authorlink=Peter H. Wilson|title=Heart of Europe|year=2016|publisher=Harvard University Press|isbn=9780674058095|ref=harv}}\n{{refend}}\n\n===Online references===\n{{refbegin|25em}}\n* {{cite web|title=Schlossweihnachtsmarkt Bruchsal|url=https://www.schlossweihnacht-bruchsal.de/|publisher=Schlossweihnachtsmarkt Bruchsal|accessdate=29 January 2019|ref={{sfnref|Schlossweihnachtsmarkt Bruchsal}}}}\n{{refend}}\n\n;German Federal and Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg State governments (in German)