ebsite] of the Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg Ministry of Tourism\n* {{in lang|de}} [http://www.dmm-bruchsal.de/Musikautomaten-Museum-Sch.49.0.html Website of the ''Deutsches Musikautomaten-Museum'']\n* {{in lang|de}} [http://bruchsaler-schlosskonzerte.de/index.php/de/ Website of the Bruchsal Palace Concerts] (not used yet)\n* {{in lang|de}} [https://www.bildindex.de/ete?action=queryupdate&desc=schloss%20bruchsal%20&index=obj-all Search results for \"Schloss Bruchsal\"] on Bildindex Der Kunst & Architektur\n* {{in lang|de}} [https://www.monumente-im-bild.de/ Website with a large collection of images about Bruchsal Palace]\n\n{{Castles in Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Palaces in Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg]]\n[[Category:Museums in Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg]]\n[[Category:Musical instrument museums in Germany]]\n[[Category:Music museums in Germany]]\n", "name_user": "John of Reading", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eHofkirche:Typo fixing, replaced: painted painted \u2192 painted", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Schloss_Bruchsal"}
