r\" |Postman Pat's Windy Day (Episode 8), Postman Pat's Tractor Express (Episode 11), The Sheep in the Clover Field (Episode 2), Postman Pat And The Magpie Hen (Episode 4), Postman Pat's Thirsty Day (Episode 7),\n|-\n| ''Postman Pat 1 Re-Release'' (BBCV 4028)\n| align=\"center\" |2 November 1992\n| align=\"center\" |Postman Pat's Finding Day (Episode 1), The Sheep in the Clover Field (Episode 2), Letters on Ice (Episode 3)\n|-\n| ''Postman Pat 2 Re-Release'' (BBCV 4029)\n| align=\"center\" |2 November 1992\n| align=\"center\"|Postman Pat and the Magpie Hen (Episode 4), Postman Pat's Foggy Day (Episode 5), Postman Pat Goes Sledging (Episode 6)\n|-\n| ''Postman Pat 3 Re-Release'' (BBCV 4030)\n| align=\"center\"|2 November 1992\n| align=\"center\"| Postman Pat's Thirsty Day (Episode 7), Postman Pat's Windy Day (Episode 8), Postman Pat's Difficult Day (Episode 9)\n|-\n| ''Postman Pat's Big Video (1992 Re-Release)'' (BBCV 4168)\n| align=\"center\"|2 November 1992\n| align=\"center\"|Postman Pat's Rainy Day (Episode 10), Postman Pat's Tractor Express (Episode 11), Postman Pat's Birthday (Episode 12), Postman Pat Takes a Message (Episode 13)\n|-\n| ''Postman Pat: Postman Pat and The Toy Soldiers Re-Release'' (BBCV 4691)\n| align=\"center\"|4 July 1994\n| align=\"center\"|Postman Pat Takes the Bus (Episode 14), Postman Pat and the Toy Soldiers (Episode 15),\n|-\n| ''Postman Pat: Postman Pat's Birthday and other stories'' (BBCV 5468)\n| align=\"center\"|5 September 1994\n| align=\"center\"| Postman Pat's Birthday (Episode 10), Letters on Ice (Episode 11), Postman Pat's Windy Day (Episode 12), Postman Pat's Foggy Day (Episode 13)\n|-\n| ''Postman Pat: Postman Pat Takes a Message and other stories'' (BBCV 5469)\n| align=\"center\"|5 September 1994\n| align=\"center\"| Postman Pat Takes a Message (Episode 6), Postman Pat's Thirsty Day (Episode 7), Postman Pat Goes Sledging (Episode 8), The Sheep in the Clover Field (Episode 9)\n|-\n| ''Postman Pat: Postman Pat's Finding Day and